# Live-generated artifacts that should be created by the viewer, not committed
# (the write-notion-report Skill, /schedule routine config)
# Note: pattern is `.claude/skills/*` (not `.claude/skills/`) so git still
# descends into the directory; a trailing-slash directory ignore short-circuits
# git's traversal and the negations below would never apply (verified empirically
# 2026-05-25 against git 2.x — see Rule-1 deviation in 01-01-SUMMARY.md).
.claude/skills/*
# Phase 1: ship the write-notion-report Skill so the repo has a working Notion
# writer out of the box. Other Skills under .claude/skills/ remain live-built
# during the video and stay ignored.
!.claude/skills/write-notion-report/
!.claude/skills/write-notion-report/**
routine_config.json
